section.para:
Field type:
... typedef int (*add_pua_event_t)(int ev_flag, char* name, char* content_type,evs_process_body_t* process_body);
- ev_flag : an event flag defined as a macro in pua module - name : the event name to be used in Event request headers - content_type: the default content_type for Publish body for that event (NULL if winfo event) - process_body: function that processes the received body before using it to construct the PUBLISH request (NULL if winfo event) ...

